reviewText: My sister & I grew up watching this movie. I love it. It came in great conditions & it was perfectly sealed.

We picked this up at a garage sale and were very pleasantly surprised.  It's really cute, funny, and even enjoyable for young-at-heart grownups to watch.  I would like to get some others in this series, as my kids and I really liked this one.
Puss in Boots is my favorite movie its fun,funny, cute,and I liked the music to. I've watched it many times and to me it gets better eatch time. In short YOU GOTTA SEE THIS MOVIE!
